 librefs13  - read-only ReFS library
 refs-dkms  - ReFS filesystem kernel modules for Linux
 refs-fuse  - Read-only ReFS FUSE driver,
 refs-fuse-default - Read-only ReFS FUSE driver (default handler for refs volumes),
 refsprogs  - Read-only ReFS progs,
 refsprogs-udeb - Read-only ReFS FUSE driver and progs, (udeb)
